title: Minefighter
content: Minefighter is a type of profession which specializes in combat in the third region of Mine of Mantuban. It focuses on unlocking higher strength monsters to fight and allows the player to wield higher level weapons and armor. Players will be unable to attack monsters with a higher Minefighter level, and likewise will be unable to equip weapons and armor with a higher Minefighter level.
